To run:
npm install
npm run dev

Controls:

Right mouse: Rotate
Left mouse: Pan
Scroll Wheel: Zoom in/ out
H: show heatmaps
J: show heatmap raycasters
S: show sun/ directional light helper
L: show computation for light intensity
Left Click on building: Select building
Left click with building selected: Deselect/ drop building
Right click with building selected: Clone building
Delete/ d with building selected: Delete building

You will also need to open the DevTools to read the values for the landmark visibility. To do this press f12 on the keyboard and go to the console panel.
Alternatively, you can go to Chrome options, more tools and DevTools to find it.
